      "content": "i hear you, but i really just want to avoid the hospital trip if i can. if it's just my asthma acting up a bit because i am getting older, can i just take an extra puff of my albuterol every few hours to compensate? like, would it be okay to just double up on my usual dose until i have time to make an appointment next month?",
